txt.en: 'Bilbo Baggins awaits! Go with haste and free him from the dungeons! At last this adventure will soon be ended, but only once he is returned unharmed to the surface!'
'You have to hurry and rescue Bilbo from Goblin-town! Are you ready to find the dungeons and free our hobbit?'
09. The Further Adventures of Bilbo Baggins, Chapter 9
Bilbo Baggins has run afoul of the goblins of the Misty Mountains... again!
Complete 'Mission: The Further Adventures of Bilbo Baggins, Chapter 9'
The monster commander in this mission has an aura that buffs any allies nearby.
Your mission is to free Bilbo Baggins from the goblins. Speak to Celeblír to set forth!
Celeblír is west of the Last Homely House, near the Town Crier.
'This endeavour is almost finished, [placeholder], but not yet. It is one thing to get into Goblin-town... but getting out is another matter!'
